{'title': "TRUMP'S most CHAOTIC press conference ending has everyone SPEECHLESS", 'uploader': 'Diario AS', 'upload_date': '20260406', 'duration': 229, 'view_count': 466269, 'like_count': 6444, 'dislike_count': None, 'comment_count': 5100, 'transcript': [{'text': 'Mr.', 'start': 0.0, 'duration': 3.2, 'end': 3.2, 'timecode': '00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.200'}, {'text': 'President, you voiced your displeasure', 'start': 0.8, 'duration': 4.84, 'end': 5.64, 'timecode': '00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:05.640'}, {'text': 'with NATO in the past. Is there a danger', 'start': 3.2, 'duration': 5.36, 'end': 8.56, 'timecode': '00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:08.560'}, {'text': 'to the US not being the de facto of the', 'start': 5.64, 'duration': 4.96, 'end': 10.6, 'timecode': '00:00:05.640 --> 00:00:10.600'}, {'text': 'leader of the alliance and then other', 'start': 8.56, 'duration': 4.0, 'end': 12.56, 'timecode': '00:00:08.560 --> 00:00:12.560'}, {'text': 'powers within the alliance then getting', 'start': 10.6, 'duration': 3.8, 'end': 14.399999999999999, 'timecode': '00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:14.400'}, {'text': 'the decision-making when it comes to', 'start': 12.56, 'duration': 3.24, 'end': 15.8, 'timecode': '00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:15.800'}, {'text': 'wars and nuclear weapons?', 'start': 14.4, 'duration': 4.16, 'end': 18.560000000000002, 'timecode': '00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:18.560'}, {'text': ">> it's not a danger. NATO's Look, we went", 'start': 15.8, 'duration': 4.12, 'end': 19.92, 'timecode': '00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:19.920'}, {'text': 'to NATO.', 'start': 18.56, 'duration': 3.36, 'end': 21.919999999999998, 'timecode': '00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:21.920'}, {'text': "I didn't ask very strongly. I just said,", 'start': 19.92, 'duration': 3.6, 'end': 23.520000000000003, 'timecode': '00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:23.520'}, {'text': '"Hey, if you want to help, great." No,', 'start': 21.92, 'duration': 3.64, 'end': 25.560000000000002, 'timecode': '00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:25.560'}, {'text': 'no, no, we will not help. I said,', 'start': 23.52, 'duration': 3.08, 'end': 26.6, 'timecode': '00:00:23.520 --> 00:00:26.600'}, {'text': '"That\'s all right. You don\'t want to', 'start': 25.56, 'duration': 3.2, 'end': 28.759999999999998, 'timecode': '00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:28.760'}, {'text': 'help." Cuz I\'ve always said NATO is a', 'start': 26.6, 'duration': 3.76, 'end': 30.36, 'timecode': '00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:30.360'}, {'text': 'paper tiger.', 'start': 28.76, 'duration': 4.16, 'end': 32.92, 'timecode': '00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:32.920'}, {'text': 'See, NATO is a paper tiger.', 'start': 30.36, 'duration': 4.36, 'end': 34.72, 'timecode': '00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:34.720'}, {'text': "Putin's not afraid of NATO. Putin's", 'start': 32.92, 'duration': 4.32, 'end': 37.24, 'timecode': '00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:37.240'}, {'text': 'afraid of us, very afraid of us.', 'start': 34.72, 'duration': 4.08, 'end': 38.8, 'timecode': '00:00:34.720 --> 00:00:38.800'}, {'text': "And he's explained it to me a lot of", 'start': 37.24, 'duration': 3.32, 'end': 40.56, 'timecode': '00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:40.560'}, {'text': 'times. I got to know him very well. I', 'start': 38.8, 'duration': 3.32, 'end': 42.12, 'timecode': '00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:42.120'}, {'text': 'know him very well.', 'start': 40.56, 'duration': 5.04, 'end': 45.6, 'timecode': '00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:45.600'}, {'text': 'Uh NATO is a paper tiger. NATO is us.', 'start': 42.12, 'duration': 5.32, 'end': 47.44, 'timecode': '00:00:42.120 --> 00:00:47.440'}, {'text': "And when we needed them, but we didn't", 'start': 45.6, 'duration': 3.52, 'end': 49.120000000000005, 'timecode': '00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:49.120'}, {'text': 'need them, by the way.', 'start': 47.44, 'duration': 3.72, 'end': 51.16, 'timecode': '00:00:47.440 --> 00:00:51.160'}, {'text': "We didn't need them, obviously, cuz they", 'start': 49.12, 'duration': 3.68, 'end': 52.8, 'timecode': '00:00:49.120 --> 00:00:52.800'}, {'text': "haven't helped at all. Just the", 'start': 51.16, 'duration': 3.2, 'end': 54.36, 'timecode': '00:00:51.160 --> 00:00:54.360'}, {'text': "opposite. They've actually gone out of", 'start': 52.8, 'duration': 3.4, 'end': 56.199999999999996, 'timecode': '00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:56.200'}, {'text': "their way not to help. They didn't even", 'start': 54.36, 'duration': 4.72, 'end': 59.08, 'timecode': '00:00:54.360 --> 00:00:59.080'}, {'text': 'want to give us landing strips.', 'start': 56.2, 'duration': 5.0, 'end': 61.2, 'timecode': '00:00:56.200 --> 00:01:01.200'}, {'text': "Think of it. And it's not just NATO. You", 'start': 59.08, 'duration': 3.96, 'end': 63.04, 'timecode': '00:00:59.080 --> 00:01:03.040'}, {'text': "know who else didn't help us? South", 'start': 61.2, 'duration': 3.88, 'end': 65.08, 'timecode': '00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:05.080'}, {'text': "Korea didn't help us. You know who else", 'start': 63.04, 'duration': 4.84, 'end': 67.88, 'timecode': '00:01:03.040 --> 00:01:07.880'}, {'text': "didn't help us? Australia didn't help", 'start': 65.08, 'duration': 4.76, 'end': 69.84, 'timecode': '00:01:05.080 --> 00:01:09.840'}, {'text': "us. You know who else didn't help us?", 'start': 67.88, 'duration': 3.92, 'end': 71.8, 'timecode': '00:01:07.880 --> 00:01:11.800'}, {'text': 'Japan.', 'start': 69.84, 'duration': 5.2, 'end': 75.04, 'timecode': '00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:15.040'}, {'text': "We've got 50,000 soldiers in Japan", 'start': 71.8, 'duration': 5.24, 'end': 77.03999999999999, 'timecode': '00:01:11.800 --> 00:01:17.040'}, {'text': 'to protect them from North Korea. We', 'start': 75.04, 'duration': 6.56, 'end': 81.60000000000001, 'timecode': '00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:21.600'}, {'text': 'have 45,000 soldiers in South Korea', 'start': 77.04, 'duration': 7.28, 'end': 84.32000000000001, 'timecode': '00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:24.320'}, {'text': 'to protect us from Kim Jong-un, who I', 'start': 81.6, 'duration': 4.24, 'end': 85.83999999999999, 'timecode': '00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:25.840'}, {'text': 'get along with very well, as you know.', 'start': 84.32, 'duration': 3.16, 'end': 87.47999999999999, 'timecode': '00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:27.480'}, {'text': 'Do you notice he said very nice things', 'start': 85.84, 'duration': 4.36, 'end': 90.2, 'timecode': '00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:30.200'}, {'text': 'about me? He used to call uh Joe Biden a', 'start': 87.48, 'duration': 5.52, 'end': 93.0, 'timecode': '00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:33.000'}, {'text': 'mentally person, okay? So,', 'start': 90.2, 'duration': 5.44, 'end': 95.64, 'timecode': '00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:35.640'}, {'text': "don't tell me about your stuff.", 'start': 93.0, 'duration': 4.12, 'end': 97.12, 'timecode': '00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:37.120'}, {'text': "Joe Biden, he said he's a mentally", 'start': 95.64, 'duration': 3.76, 'end': 99.4, 'timecode': '00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:39.400'}, {'text': ' person. He was so nasty to Joe', 'start': 97.12, 'duration': 4.28, 'end': 101.4, 'timecode': '00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:41.400'}, {'text': 'Biden. It was terrible. But to me, he', 'start': 99.4, 'duration': 4.84, 'end': 104.24000000000001, 'timecode': '00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:44.240'}, {'text': 'likes Trump. And do you notice how nice', 'start': 101.4, 'duration': 4.12, 'end': 105.52000000000001, 'timecode': '00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:45.520'}, {'text': "things are with North Korea? It's very", 'start': 104.24, 'duration': 2.32, 'end': 106.55999999999999, 'timecode': '00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:46.560'}, {'text': 'nice.', 'start': 105.52, 'duration': 4.76, 'end': 110.28, 'timecode': '00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:50.280'}, {'text': 'But we have 45,000 people soldiers in', 'start': 106.56, 'duration': 6.44, 'end': 113.0, 'timecode': '00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:53.000'}, {'text': "harm's way and right next to Kim Jong-un", 'start': 110.28, 'duration': 4.8, 'end': 115.08, 'timecode': '00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:55.080'}, {'text': 'with a lot of nuclear weapons.', 'start': 113.0, 'duration': 4.6, 'end': 117.6, 'timecode': '00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:57.600'}, {'text': '45 which should have never happened', 'start': 115.08, 'duration': 4.68, 'end': 119.75999999999999, 'timecode': '00:01:55.080 --> 00:01:59.760'}, {'text': "if a certain president, I'm not going to", 'start': 117.6, 'duration': 3.48, 'end': 121.08, 'timecode': '00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:01.080'}, {'text': 'mention this president cuz I happen to', 'start': 119.76, 'duration': 3.2, 'end': 122.96000000000001, 'timecode': '00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:02.960'}, {'text': 'like him, believe it or not. But if a', 'start': 121.08, 'duration': 4.48, 'end': 125.56, 'timecode': '00:02:01.080 --> 00:02:05.560'}, {'text': 'certain president did his job, Kim', 'start': 122.96, 'duration': 4.4, 'end': 127.36, 'timecode': '00:02:02.960 --> 00:02:07.360'}, {'text': 'Jong-un would not have nuclear weapons', 'start': 125.56, 'duration': 3.4, 'end': 128.96, 'timecode': '00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:08.960'}, {'text': "right now. But they're all afraid to do", 'start': 127.36, 'duration': 3.44, 'end': 130.8, 'timecode': '00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:10.800'}, {'text': 'their job properly.', 'start': 128.96, 'duration': 5.6, 'end': 134.56, 'timecode': '00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:14.560'}, {'text': 'But just to conclude and just to finish,', 'start': 130.8, 'duration': 5.96, 'end': 136.76000000000002, 'timecode': '00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:16.760'}, {'text': "Japan didn't help us, Australia didn't", 'start': 134.56, 'duration': 5.0, 'end': 139.56, 'timecode': '00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:19.560'}, {'text': "help us, South Korea didn't help us. And", 'start': 136.76, 'duration': 4.68, 'end': 141.44, 'timecode': '00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:21.440'}, {'text': "then you get to NATO, NATO didn't help", 'start': 139.56, 'duration': 3.96, 'end': 143.52, 'timecode': '00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:23.520'}, {'text': 'us. There were some countries that did.', 'start': 141.44, 'duration': 4.08, 'end': 145.52, 'timecode': '00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:25.520'}, {'text': 'Now, countries that have been good, now', 'start': 143.52, 'duration': 3.76, 'end': 147.28, 'timecode': '00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:27.280'}, {'text': "you could also say they're", 'start': 145.52, 'duration': 3.04, 'end': 148.56, 'timecode': '00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:28.560'}, {'text': 'got to be a little bit more involved', 'start': 147.28, 'duration': 2.92, 'end': 150.2, 'timecode': '00:02:27.280 --> 00:02:30.200'}, {'text': "because they're in the territory. But", 'start': 148.56, 'duration': 4.08, 'end': 152.64000000000001, 'timecode': '00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:32.640'}, {'text': "Saudi Arabia's been excellent. Qatar's", 'start': 150.2, 'duration': 5.6, 'end': 155.79999999999998, 'timecode': '00:02:30.200 --> 00:02:35.800'}, {'text': 'been excellent. UAE has been excellent.', 'start': 152.64, 'duration': 5.16, 'end': 157.79999999999998, 'timecode': '00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:37.800'}, {'text': 'Bahrain, Kuwait, I mean, Kuwait did', 'start': 155.8, 'duration': 4.36, 'end': 160.16000000000003, 'timecode': '00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:40.160'}, {'text': 'shoot down three of our planes. The only', 'start': 157.8, 'duration': 4.76, 'end': 162.56, 'timecode': '00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:42.560'}, {'text': 'planes really that we lost were', 'start': 160.16, 'duration': 4.4, 'end': 164.56, 'timecode': '00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:44.560'}, {'text': 'friendly fire, they called it. I call it', 'start': 162.56, 'duration': 3.68, 'end': 166.24, 'timecode': '00:02:42.560 --> 00:02:46.240'}, {'text': 'unfriendly fire.', 'start': 164.56, 'duration': 3.4, 'end': 167.96, 'timecode': '00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:47.960'}, {'text': "They unfortunately didn't know how to", 'start': 166.24, 'duration': 3.48, 'end': 169.72, 'timecode': '00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:49.720'}, {'text': 'use our', 'start': 167.96, 'duration': 4.64, 'end': 172.6, 'timecode': '00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:52.600'}, {'text': 'our great Patriots.', 'start': 169.72, 'duration': 4.12, 'end': 173.84, 'timecode': '00:02:49.720 --> 00:02:53.840'}, {'text': 'The pilots said, "What kind of a', 'start': 172.6, 'duration': 3.56, 'end': 176.16, 'timecode': '00:02:52.600 --> 00:02:56.160'}, {'text': 'missile\'s coming at us?" Patriot. Boom.', 'start': 173.84, 'duration': 3.92, 'end': 177.76, 'timecode': '00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:57.760'}, {'text': 'They got out.', 'start': 176.16, 'duration': 3.96, 'end': 180.12, 'timecode': '00:02:56.160 --> 00:03:00.120'}, {'text': 'Because they know Patriot never misses.', 'start': 177.76, 'duration': 4.68, 'end': 182.44, 'timecode': '00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:02.440'}, {'text': 'So, they had beautiful Patriots. There', 'start': 180.12, 'duration': 4.88, 'end': 185.0, 'timecode': '00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:05.000'}, {'text': 'were planes heading in their direction.', 'start': 182.44, 'duration': 4.8, 'end': 187.24, 'timecode': '00:03:02.440 --> 00:03:07.240'}, {'text': 'Unfortunately, they decided to shoot', 'start': 185.0, 'duration': 4.8, 'end': 189.8, 'timecode': '00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:09.800'}, {'text': 'those planes. They were our planes. So,', 'start': 187.24, 'duration': 4.04, 'end': 191.28, 'timecode': '00:03:07.240 --> 00:03:11.280'}, {'text': 'uh', 'start': 189.8, 'duration': 3.76, 'end': 193.56, 'timecode': '00:03:09.800 --> 00:03:13.560'}, {'text': 'No, NATO is a paper tiger.', 'start': 191.28, 'duration': 4.28, 'end': 195.56, 'timecode': '00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:15.560'}, {'text': "Now, he's coming to see me on Wednesday,", 'start': 193.56, 'duration': 4.52, 'end': 198.08, 'timecode': '00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:18.080'}, {'text': "as you know. He's a wonderful guy.", 'start': 195.56, 'duration': 4.8, 'end': 200.36, 'timecode': '00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:20.360'}, {'text': 'Secretary General is great.', 'start': 198.08, 'duration': 4.28, 'end': 202.36, 'timecode': '00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:22.360'}, {'text': 'And Mark Rutte', 'start': 200.36, 'duration': 3.96, 'end': 204.32000000000002, 'timecode': '00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:24.320'}, {'text': 'is a great person, but', 'start': 202.36, 'duration': 3.8, 'end': 206.16000000000003, 'timecode': '00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:26.160'}, {'text': "he's got And you know, it all began", 'start': 204.32, 'duration': 3.48, 'end': 207.79999999999998, 'timecode': '00:03:24.320 --> 00:03:27.800'}, {'text': 'with, if you want to know the truth,', 'start': 206.16, 'duration': 3.08, 'end': 209.24, 'timecode': '00:03:26.160 --> 00:03:29.240'}, {'text': 'Greenland.', 'start': 207.8, 'duration': 3.36, 'end': 211.16000000000003, 'timecode': '00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:31.160'}, {'text': "We want Greenland. They don't want to", 'start': 209.24, 'duration': 4.84, 'end': 214.08, 'timecode': '00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:34.080'}, {'text': 'give it to us and I said, "Bye-bye."', 'start': 211.16, 'duration': 5.08, 'end': 216.24, 'timecode': '00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:36.240'}, {'text': 'Okay, thank you very much, everybody.', 'start': 214.08, 'duration': 4.44, 'end': 218.52, 'timecode': '00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:38.520'}, {'text': 'Thank you.', 'start': 216.24, 'duration': 2.28, 'end': 218.52, 'timecode': '00:03:36.240 --> 00:03:38.520'}, {'text': 'What about rising gas prices for', 'start': 221.72, 'duration': 3.6, 'end': 225.32, 'timecode': '00:03:41.720 --> 00:03:45.320'}, {'text': 'Americans? What are your concerns?', 'start': 223.56, 'duration': 4.12, 'end': 227.68, 'timecode': '00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:47.680'}, {'text': 'General', 'start': 225.32, 'duration': 2.36, 'end': 227.68, 'timecode': '00:03:45.320 --> 00:03:47.680'}]}